  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV89">
<l>tīviṉaikkaru nañcai nalviṉaik kiṉṉa mutattiṉaip</l>
<l>pūviṉai mēviya tēvi maṇāḷaṉaip puṉmaiyeḷkā</l>
<l>tāviṉai mēykkum vallāyaṉai yaṉṟula kīraṭiyāṟ</l>
<l>ṟāviṉa vēṟṟaiyem māṉaiyeñ ñāṉṟu talaippeyvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The rare poison to evil deeds, the sweet ambrosia to good deeds,</l>
<l>the bridegroom of the goddess who dwells in the flower, the strong cowherd</l>
<l>who grazes [his] cow without slighting [its] lowliness, the bull who with [his]</l> 
<l>two feet leapt over the world that day, our lord, when shall I meet him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
